➜笔记收藏！“十四五”，信息通信业要这么干
http://www.sohu.com/a/429813777_354877	49022
<p><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201106/1c99f97c2e174fa2a84899bb51ba4220.png" /></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201106/6bd7b42b2496404e90e4a664ce6695c6.png" /></p>
